PiOnAPi - Calculate the constant Pi on a Raspberry Pi

Use a streaming (spigot) algorigthm to compute the digits of Pi.

Dependencies:

pyfiglet - pip install git+https://github.com/pwaller/pyfiglet
termcolor - pip install termcolor

Pip is used for ease of installation, but if it is not installed on your machine a guide can be found here.
https://pip.pypa.io/en/stable/installing/
